<br>
Fankly its getting the point with the amount of CC in the game that if I dont land my CD, I am as good as stunned and then killed. Its great fun to be instant stun'd by hib casters that can nuke me for 500-700 pts of damage every couple seconds, or if in some miracle I manage to avoid being stunned, I then get bolted by the same caster for 660 damage every couple secs. I run up to a caster and PA, my big one shot attack, for 300, and then get nuked for 600. The way epic armor resists are, I actually on average PA tanks for more then I PA casters for. <br>
<br>
Not to mention my PAs do generally speaking 'less' then first aid 1 will heal on a level 50 target in epic armor. <br>
<br>
Couple all that with a billion GTAOE and PBAOE on every climbing route, doors of milegates, open areas between forces, and the role of the 'assassin' is pretty much disappearing at an exponential rate.<br>
